All Implemented Interfaces:
CodeNode.Listener, Decaf, Serializable, Typed, Utils.Renderable
public abstract class TypeOfficer
extends EnforcementOfficer
implements Typed

This specialization of EnforcementOfficer maintains the current type of the Grammar it patrols. Often it is convenient for a GrammarMask to defer its type resolution to a TypeOfficer, so that the rules for resolution and the means of identifying internal Type-related chaos reside in the same class.
